=== Failed bids ===
'''{{NOR}}'''{{Snd}}A Norwegian request to buy PrSM was turned down by U.S. authorities in August 2024, due to export restrictions at the time.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-08-26 |title=U.S. denies sale of PrSM and ER GMLRS missiles to Norway |url=https://defence-industry.eu/u-s-denies-sale-of-prsm-and-er-gmlrs-missiles-to-norway/ |access-date=2024-08-28 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2024-10-03 |title=Lockheed Martin bekrefter til TU: Jobber for å tilby nytt langdistansemissil internasjonalt |url=https://www.tu.no/artikler/lockheed-martin-bekrefter-til-tu-jobber-for-a-tilby-nytt-langdistanse-missil-internasjonalt/551420 |access-date=2026-04-03 |language=no}}(paywall)</ref> A simultaneous request for [[ATACMS|M57 ATACMS]] and [[M142 HIMARS]] launchers was however approved <ref>https://media.defense.gov/2024/Dec/09/2003604142/-1/-1/0/PRESS%20RELEASE%20-%20NORWAY%2024-75%20CN.PDF</ref>, but both were ultimately turned down in favor of the South Korean [[K239 Chunmoo]] with associated missiles<ref>https://www.fma.no/en/news-and-media/newsarticles/new-contract-with-hanwha-aerospace-to-procure-long-range-precision-fires</ref>.

